The paper focuses on image and video caption retrieval using textual input, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of deep neural networks for feature extraction also suggests a potential overlap with multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the evaluation of state-of-the-art results indicates a possible connection to machine learning (cs.LG).
